  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 박스와 어울리는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>쇼핑백 주문</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b215b302-afbe-47ab-bb09-59a0e71e7c2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2bd69b48-e5bf-453c-a035-e1be0679a636\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d895b74e-33c4-45cb-8e0d-aa96c514b2a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3cf5d291-ed5a-4c42-a943-fceb44b17877\" style=\"\">목업사이트 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">쇼핑백의 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">쇼핑백에서 가장 많이 사용되는 종이는 아트지/스노우지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d3161b6-2340-4271-b78d-c62655fa90e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d996b9bf-3238-4857-b9be-e23250629328\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17249f77-b060-44d1-8dc1-e4834101a4e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e9c7f39-b845-44db-b0f7-31bb051642ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">카탈로그 종이도 아트지/스노우지가 대표적이지만 쇼핑백도 가장 많이 사용되는 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddf4a1e9-6af1-4a89-a476-1cc375dabe9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fec7c1c8-542e-462f-a140-487fa05e3e1d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9913406f-1713-40fb-9b03-508316f8a54a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc46280c-47aa-4b89-ba77-838b967ab2f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아트지는 스노우지와 다른 점이 반짝거리는 유광이고 반대로 스노우지는 무광이며 아트지보다 약간 더 두터운 감이 있습니다. 발색이 좋고 어떠한 후공정도 잘 처리할 수 있는 종이라서 대표적인 쇼핑백 종이라고 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-04f8dc59-b051-481d-9113-b26efe206dbb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c35d5a8c-8fea-486b-9961-23e1e2b6a9f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dfadb741-1cf7-4ac7-9e9b-a24a19b64a34\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b4c2cbd-feeb-45fa-8cc3-c79e4dc2f1ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 소프트하고 매끄러운 종이가 있는 반면에 약간은 러프한 계열의 종이들도 있습니다. 가장 대표적으로 모조지, 랑데뷰나 아르떼지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0455c5f3-3466-4d85-a9f8-451f3e568897\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01291086-a693-4726-baf4-8a261e24f0ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0017d95-9e35-452d-b04d-017fd30bc791\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-561ff104-4bc1-4332-bf98-d51ec067a9c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모조지, 랑데뷰나 아르떼 종이는 국산지로 비교적 가격이 저렴하고 아트지처럼 맨들 거리는 느낌이 싫으신 분들이 선호합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9413dbc2-5006-4996-8b56-fb305a9c79b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81411466-b283-4607-b815-b5c2d9f7daa5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b5fdb69-46bb-477f-b7fe-30ca8c8db7ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3224e9ea-4081-43d5-9f0a-ae28ee21d25e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 코팅으로 처리하기 나쁘고 아트지나 스노우지에 비해 경제성이나 실제 쇼핑백이 나오면 실효성 면에서 특별한 경우를 제외하고는 아트/스노우지에 비해 제작이 덜한 편입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-726914d8-af56-4617-81fa-62908d48119a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be2b725e-e1a4-4691-b968-2bfe02455cd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0e0eecac-0074-405d-8111-a372a421099a\" style=\"\">패턴지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-50bdd954-61ca-4cd2-bef9-9bf8e5a882da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-414fbabb-37ec-4a1f-9175-e29490385132\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e98081f7-bb60-468c-aa5b-5ce69b76c6fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가격은 좀 비싸지만 평범한 종이가 아닌 특별한 종이를 선호할 경우는 크라프트나 색지 또는 흑기사처럼 흑지를 사용하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8aa743d5-8a6c-48ea-9759-c41deae4f279\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb65417b-c7ad-4556-9fd5-35cdb7754d0e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a7324727-87ce-4022-ae02-1922bb7fd93f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9dcff738-bedf-468c-a4dc-acac2194f78b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 스타드림이나 시리오 시리즈처럼 펄지로 더 특별한 쇼핑백을 만들 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68f37231-e17f-4bd7-91a0-e4513d7879f4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d208919-f7f8-4111-b092-d82b2eef7863\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0e5b3236-10a6-45f9-825d-326b0d27b869\" style=\"\">삼원페이퍼 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-736859eb-9dde-41ab-bc9f-eede73b2fa8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f694ea01-59a9-4249-8c67-6346d47200d3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d8e0c74-f5b2-4d39-ad64-c0a84313c512\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지는 친환경 종이의 대표적인 케이스로 특별한 쇼핑백으로 가장 많이 제작되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f285021b-f2df-4d4a-9d99-e613e4d55d38\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/004.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39164670-0387-4b64-9d17-b7c81545fa73\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b9dcf36a-e872-4ecd-bcae-62783d088f5e\" style=\"\">크라프트</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96838012-6463-495f-8fb3-a2df6b3c8405\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cdc9f5a0-1301-44c1-aa6a-b1a726781e70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3bf5c67d-6ac1-4a5d-9982-aabe66f6e3fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지는 종류나 다양하지만 가격이 경제적이지는 않습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cfaaa763-52c6-48aa-8e8c-9ac0c1bd2e04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e969fb6-3fa4-499d-8c97-7a9dd90fc5a1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-67030963-5b1a-45d1-a9ce-5caefd9b4b19\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7fdf1f73-de0f-4c8c-8028-19aaea54eb56\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>쇼핑백에 가장 적당한 종이 평량은?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2d10248-9bff-452d-b9e9-50b73f83dd31\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-042095c7-7f2b-48d0-be30-34ef879bd676\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78fdf059-532d-4650-bd9c-4dcf31223c7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4a6522b-9f60-435c-a970-def3dce80bc5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백 제작 시 가장 적당한 두께는 어느 정도일까요? 기준은 다르지만 일반적으로는 180g ~ 250g 사이가 가장 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-efc1c1a0-4387-4bb7-8c70-bf1b3c2f0b45\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88ca4221-9532-4dde-b047-5b610b02ed6f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8fa15c90-65ea-4841-ab4e-a8f3ca603d98\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8494eb5a-14ff-4db9-a137-e7c35a2028b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">180g은 조금은 얇다는 느낌의 두께입니다. 하지만 이 평량도 종이에 따라 두께감이 다르기 때문에 획일적으로 정의할 수는 없습니다. 그리고 코팅 유무에 따라서도 달라집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45b9d72a-9e8b-4d15-b838-70229a36860a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a9629e8-5c94-4d4b-ba9a-6dac2cf9cce0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ba61bbc-3f19-43d3-a859-84ebcda2e5b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ab20b1f5-9c67-462d-ba8c-070eb8f1bf3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">200g 이 넘어가고 250g 정도가 되면 약간 두꺼운 느낌의 쇼핑백 두께라고 생각하시면 됩니다. 그 이상의 두께는 거의 사용되지 않습니다. 두꺼우면 목형과 톰슨(도무송)과정에서 잘 안 따지거나 안 접힐 수 있으므로 가급적 선택하지 않으십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3dc2831-7911-49da-9d74-866bb314c7d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4577c9b4-e3a4-4c29-acd1-6b7d12d9b4db\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04c34994-77b8-46a0-bf5b-e5591440895b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-04c0eba2-eb41-4335-b2d2-da4cc86b39f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>200g을 기준으로 얇고 두꺼운 느낌으로 원하시는 대로 제작하시면 좋습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a25ac2fd-6755-4302-b537-bcef2ed701c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b6a7d8d-876d-4393-af93-e28315b6d080\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4f13556e-5f2b-4c46-8ce8-e9caebd859f9\" style=\"\">쇼핑백의 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca5c9711-8e73-41f0-86db-ae2c342df7e2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1a235d4-8f9a-4612-b1f5-4e5e5668dcf9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b50b675-5b97-4692-b668-c12246df192d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">쇼핑백은 복잡한 디자인이 거의 없고 로고나 브랜드 컬러를 이용한 배경색으로 마무리하는 경우가 대부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-06cf15aa-7212-4d5c-bfb0-ef800c94ef1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1e3ae51-42d6-4036-a565-071c422c3591\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c19542e3-e946-4f21-846b-72adea4842bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-613ea3bb-b3ec-4ebc-8fc8-87d73df10956\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아닌 경우도 있지만 대부분 로고만 양쪽에 넣고 디자인을 정리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-447a0f72-557c-42ee-84b9-4aca7a995938\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-297c00a2-cb9c-44a6-85f1-7d617b0c4b71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18a0d9c7-20bd-4d41-b671-377bfe3ac653\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ec4f123d-8eb7-4468-8e05-ba5c21537136\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 CMYK 4도 인쇄보다는 별색 1~2도로 마무리하거나 박인쇄, 투명 실크로 인쇄 없이 진행하는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b5f5ba4-9309-4bd3-98bb-1f55207af5b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80c1b386-cd7f-4165-af57-cab1f084123c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef704126-c88b-45bf-a63e-d9df460ff324\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-72deadb7-a331-4eb1-b0c2-a8750c6fa959\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백의 인쇄야말로 너무나 다양하고 고객의 선택 몫이 큽니다. 4도로 진행하면 일반적인 아트/스노우지로 종이를 선택하며 흑기사나 색지를 선택하는 경우에는 별색이나 후공정으로 작업을 보통 마무리하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d16cab94-de33-4530-8ade-880f09fade86\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-20282e72-dfaa-4fd3-a6b9-6e25138b7c46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 쇼핑백은 브랜드 컬러에 맞는 별색으로 진행하세요. 또는 흑지에 은별색이나 은박으로 처리하면 훨씬 고급스럽습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b2f6cdd-e9c5-4103-bd4b-eba3f2bd0c59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-2cb391b5-8452-4913-b393-d5c3abb761c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00b872fc-9f18-41ce-bda4-1ffd18330dfd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-41f5d11c-2943-4795-afb4-eb22774ab611\" style=\"\">쇼핑백의 후공정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f1b308f0-3eb3-4792-ae2e-058f9a7411ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-055f6e0c-44a2-400c-9f58-61f3457ed91d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0ce259b1-6017-40b5-a8a7-881dc177e2bc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">후공정은 박인쇄가 가장 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-81b16a1d-3632-4a87-ba7b-509faea18786\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4de212ad-bbfa-49fc-84c4-09a993d48962\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b1e8056-048d-43f8-8f23-4f4e02155624\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-886d0b5a-dfe9-432e-a056-24505c7e449d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고를 박인쇄로 진행하면 돋보이는 것뿐 아니라 훨씬 브랜드를 살릴 수 있습니다. 박인쇄에 형압은 쇼핑백에서 가장 대표적인 후공정 조합입니다. 로고만 있는 쇼핑백이라면 이 후공정으로 멋을 내보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fae97b7-0e57-401d-bf9f-dc34b9438b3b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3c7d45e-4694-4470-97d8-cc6129797fc5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76723611-da6c-4740-8224-0ebf8eb42b32\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cbf88819-9d24-4427-85fb-c428f92b9a22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 후공정 말고도 투명 UV 부분 코팅이나 에폭시 또는 전체 홀로그램 코팅으로 색다르게 후공정을 할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f2fceab-9f0e-475c-ac39-855882929884\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5af887f4-ee28-4da3-af57-3b9ba6026d36\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bb0e3191-a60d-4d53-81b5-5fe8b32f7633\" style=\"\">목업사이트 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-803932cc-f14f-48c8-99e0-c8cd459ebc08\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-569d8ab1-8691-496b-9364-0a6692aea31f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cedeec68-5976-43a6-a381-e7781f53e86d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c6295cbc-e29c-4a86-8fe9-9739068382dd\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>쇼핑백의 부자재</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd295617-56fe-46a2-9197-f66b0556a0c2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f115c08-de0d-4975-8182-f4ad23541afd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffc1bfd3-1a8e-4add-a12b-19fc52cb4f12\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09302b52-f3d0-422c-8c78-650c20adf783\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백의 부자재는 끈이 대표적입니다. 끈의 종류는 매우 다양합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-85a5ce79-7d3c-4a81-8da3-a3adf47d50bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/008.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0797998b-ad82-4aaa-b0f3-546a98cf4141\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-15f94f6a-7fa3-4931-baa7-a81a08db9263\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4c7e7e0-d9ec-408d-ae69-5b5afc0a1d36\" style=\"color:#555555;\">pp 끈에서부터 면끈, 지끈 등 너무나 다양한 끈 종류가 있습니다. 또한 철팁이나 매듭, 그리고 아일릿 등 다양한 부자재가 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e5dcff9-8aa4-4812-9422-6d75b921af34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223998718255/009.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe9895f7-72a4-4160-b10c-da6b054aa8ac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e2eb1fe7-e1fa-4c15-8a38-2d07ae9da225\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b469b5e6-c49a-4999-aa96-719d0b73744e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222900246291?trackingCode=blog_bloghome_searchlist\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222900246291?trackingCode=blog_bloghome_searchlist</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-f7fdd23c-05c3-4170-a848-6235d8924fef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b524b80-89c7-44ad-bb34-441ded128a98\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-83e12bc1-0aed-4876-94e7-62c32f9c007a\" style=\"\">결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c7b7ce2d-a49a-4ed9-9f4b-a12e1e36d1d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b378216e-eb6b-480c-a918-ccffe0aef71f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c0df6f3-c480-45af-84e0-a4fb31371748\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박스를 담는 쇼핑백은 하나의 세트처럼 인식됩니다. 대부분의 회사가 쇼핑백과 패키지를 동시에 작업하고 진행하고 있습니다. 패키지의 크기에 맞추어 맞춤 쇼핑백으로 동시 납품을 원하는 회사가 늘어나고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bc7304b-9e34-457c-9888-3d30a1470eb2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76b974a9-67f7-4e03-9e01-6fa467516b5c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b19c31df-b361-4c22-a248-e9b03e86cc8f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c420037-f3e1-4531-aea7-f76e254393c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객 여러분께서는 무조건 단가를 기준으로 의뢰하지는 마시기 바랍니다. 단가만 맞추다 보면 원하는 제품이 안 나올 수 있습니다. 반드시 상담을 통해 원하는 납기와 퀄리티는 요청하여 제작하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1df13b1f-5394-44ec-b2ab-caed3bd68ee3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0edd7522-aea1-4e1d-b821-42cd5e7bfb69\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-200403c1-68c6-409e-83bd-aed81f072e4f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09152023-b0ba-4dee-b954-10055933907a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">퀄리티와 단가가 반드시 비례하지는 않지만 대부분 싼 단가로 무조건 저렴하게만 납품하는 회사가 늘어나고 있습니다. 가장 좋은 선택은 합리적인 가격에 고객님이 원하는 퀄리티와 납기를 보장받는 길입니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니이 함께하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223998718255#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}